            <p>Team Practices are held in a specifically designed area in our main facility. Our Team Practice space was specifically designed for versatility and function, allowing coaches to adjust the nets to create many different layouts for practices. Our teams can use the space to practice live at-bats (hitter v. pitcher), set up various hitting lanes, do bullpens, or a variety of other layouts. In addition, there is also plenty of outdoor space used by our teams for additional throwing space, outfielders work and team conditioning.</p>

